{"tid":2454481,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"許樹昌：不接種第二劑疫苗尤如前功盡廢","createTime":"2021-03-20T09:18:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-21T06:55:03.000Z","uid":350584,"like":13,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"098dc5b7e483f8062ad42836afe27525f11b3544","tid":2454481,"uid":350584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T09:18:49.000Z","msg":"中大呼吸系統科講座教授許樹昌「若接種一劑疫苗，抗體會出現一段時間，但隨著時間會下跌，若不接種第二劑，基本上前功盡廢，最後都會失去保護力。至今的死亡個案大家都看清楚，很多有高危因素如心血管病，與疫苗沒有因果關係，因此大家毋須太擔心。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=428139\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D428139&d=Msg9JqZwuY5xVY%2FdQIJkDP3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=799e796a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D428139&h=9d7f2a34\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=428139</a>"},{"pid":"5b11e666b3fb12b91135a857da86b02ba46475f0","tid":2454481,"uid":350584,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T09:19:08.000Z","msg":"許樹昌又指，接種第二劑疫苗時，身體免疫反應可能較第一劑強烈，會出現較多徵狀，如疲倦和肌肉酸痛等，接種兩周後抗體水平會轉趨穩定，但市民仍要保持個人衞生。"},{"pid":"c949944c84356573c15a1416813af8cbf8b82053","tid":2454481,"uid":350584,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T09:19:53.000Z","msg":"中大呼吸系統科講座教授許樹昌：至今的死亡個案大家都看清楚，很多有高危因素如心血管病，與疫苗沒有因果關係，因此大家毋須太擔心。」"},{"pid":"79d6d267f2b63dace9d1c0f2f82effb019c0a3c4","tid":2454481,"uid":77196,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T09:20:08.000Z","msg":"廢老，第2RD生死挑戰要開始了"},{"pid":"495c5fb594be1becae98b510392993e78b2555a1","tid":2454481,"uid":350584,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T09:20:54.000Z","msg":"許樹昌上水鼓勵大家打第2針了"},{"pid":"d62ea727a56b99391d6853f9267ed9335e7f5265","tid":2454481,"uid":17443,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T09:21:07.000Z","msg":"係咪第2 ROUND好多唔見人?<br /